Responsible Provider:

Example:

Borys, Heidi L, CRNA — 13:58–19:02

Prado V, Isabel, SRNA — 13:58–19:02

Shaw, Matthew, MD — 13:58–15:30

Shi, Kevin, MD — 15:30–16:47

Podnar, Jeffrey J, MD — 16:47–17:43

Murugappan, Kadhiresan R, MD — 17:43–19:02

Here, Shaw, Matthew, MD covered the longest continuous portion of the case and should be selected as the correct provider."
